<br>
In Grimling Forest there's a safe Vah Shir outpost (where the port point is) just to the right of the zone in.  Levitation is useful here if you have it.  You'll want to keep invis up.  If you have levitation, I usually run up the right wall until the zone wall curves around to the west.  There is a grimling village in this corner, and a tunnel just behind the village leads to Tenebrous Mountains.  If you don't have levitation, you can swim up the river that runs through the forest.  It ends in a waterfall, run right from the waterfall to get to the tunnel (again, invisible, those grimlings are nasty).<br>
<br>
When you zone into Tenebrous, if you imagine the zone is a square, you are on the bottom of the square near the right corner.  The coterie fort is on the right side about 2/3 of the way up.  Beware - this is a dangerous zone (lvl 30s+ aggressive mobs) and many things see through invisibility.  Also, several things cannot be slowed or rooted.  It's quite hilly so levitation is useful.  I'd suggest you get SoW for safety also.  Tzaroth (Jinsei in game) can probably tell you more - I was timid, and stayed back at the zone since I would have been KoS, and he was too young to lose experience anyway.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Incidentally the zone in to Tenebrous from Grimling Forest is where the Grimling Runner spawns who drops the pouch that you can quest into a Rallic Pack.  He's in his low 30s.<br>
<br>
If you see me or Cata online send me a tell and Cata will happily port or translocate you to Grimling Forest and show you the way up.  I usually start playing after 1am PST on weekdays, though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=morgrist>Morgrist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 264<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/23/03 1:54:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=157.topic&index=25>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bile</span><hr size=1> Neriak Ghouls are KoS to everybody that isn't a Teir'dal. Period. I just Invis to Undead past them myself.<br>
