<br>
Lokar To'biath is between lvl 9-11. So around level 15 or so, he should be green to you, and not aggro.<br>
<br>
You'll need to take someone with you who can invis you.<br>
<br>
Hand the fellow the first 4 wine, but don't click the 'give' button yet. Have your friend invis you, which drops you back to indifferent, THEN click 'give'. I did this with an Ogre friend to fix his faction in Neriak. After the first or second hand in, you should be able to hand the rest in without an invis.<br>
<br>
Take at least a bag if not two of wine. The only faction that this quest doesn't improve is The Dead (the necro and shadowknight guild) and The Indigo Brotherhood (warriors). You can raise The Dead by killing the white robed pales out by the teleport pyramid. You can raise Indigo Brotherhood by killing elf slaves in Crushbone, as well as elves in Timorous Deep.<br>
<br>
