<br>
There is a guy who stands outside, Olavn N`Mar, and he is on The Dead faction. You are going to want to invis past him. He's not very... friendly.<br>
<br>
The faction in there is called The Spurned. It is very very hard to change your faction with them (except to make it worse).<br>
